{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:33:17.746Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Organizing a prompt library"},{"type":"text","text":" transforms your scattered prompts into a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"centralized, searchable, and reusable asset"},{"type":"text","text":" that saves time, maintains consistency, and scales prompting best practices across teams."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"The key insight:"},{"type":"text","text":" \"Prompts are the magic that makes your LLM system work. They are your secret sauce. Make sure they are organized & versioned in a CMS.\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Organize a Prompt Library?"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. Save Time Repeatedly"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You'll write a good prompt for AI and want to reuse it.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No recreation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Reuse proven prompts instead of rewriting\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quick access"},{"type":"text","text":" — Find the right prompt in seconds\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistency"},{"type":"text","text":" — Same prompt, same quality"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Standardize AI Use"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Standardise AI use, improve consistency, and save time with shared prompt engineering practices.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Organizational benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reduced variance"},{"type":"text","text":" — Everyone uses best prompts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Team alignment"},{"type":"text","text":" — Shared standards\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Training tool"},{"type":"text","text":" — Learn from library examples"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Enable Collaboration"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Make it collaborative. Let your team contribute, test, and improve prompts together.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaboration features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Team contributions"},{"type":"text","text":" — Share \"secret weapon\" prompts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Feedback loops"},{"type":"text","text":" — Suggest improvements\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Version collaboration"},{"type":"text","text":" — Track who changed what"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Categorization Strategies"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Strategy 1: Category-Based Structure"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Organize prompts by function\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Common categories:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Marketing"},{"type":"text","text":" — Copy, campaigns, social media\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Code Generation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Snippets, functions, debugging\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Data Analysis"},{"type":"text","text":" — Reports, insights, charts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Customer Support"},{"type":"text","text":" — Triaging, responses, FAQs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Content Creation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Blogs, articles, scripts\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Research Workflows"},{"type":"text","text":" — Summaries, citations, analysis\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Coding & Automation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Scripts, workflows, integrations"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example structure:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Marketing/\n  ├── Product Launch Campaign\n  ├── Social Media Post\n  ├── Email Newsletter\n  └── Ad Copy Variations\n\nCode/\n  ├── Python Function Generator\n  ├── Code Review Assistant\n  ├── Bug Fixer\n  └── Documentation Writer"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Strategy 2: Discipline: Task Naming"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"All entries follow the format: 'Discipline: Task' (e.g., Marketing: Create product launch campaign).\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Naming format:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Discipline: Task\n\nExample:\nSales: Analyze notes from intro call\nSales: Role play as buyer persona\nMarketing: Create product launch campaign\nEngineering: Write API documentation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Consistent names"},{"type":"text","text":" — Easy to scan\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Facilitates nesting"},{"type":"text","text":" — Discipline as top-level category\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Outcome-based"},{"type":"text","text":" — Tasks = outcomes, not actions"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Strategy 3: Nesting by Discipline"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"This naming format also facilitates nesting, using the assigned 'discipline' as top-level categories.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Nested structure:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sales - Sales:\n  ├── Sales: Analyze notes from intro call\n  ├── Sales: Role play as buyer persona\n  └── Sales: Sales call preparation (FAQs)\n\nMarketing - Marketing:\n  ├── Marketing: Create product launch campaign\n  ├── Marketing: Write blog post\n  └── Marketing: Design social media ads"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Top-level grouping"},{"type":"text","text":" — Discipline as folder\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hierarchical navigation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Drill down by category\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Scalable"},{"type":"text","text":" — Add new disciplines easily"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Strategy 4: Use-Case Grouping"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Group prompts into clear categories\""},{"type":"text","text":" by use case"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use case categories:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Marketing copy"},{"type":"text","text":" — Advertisements, emails, blogs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Customer support"},{"type":"text","text":" — Responses, triaging, FAQs\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Research workflows"},{"type":"text","text":" — Analysis, summaries, citations\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Coding & automation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Scripts, debugging, documentation"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Marketing Copy:\n  ├── Email for Product Launch\n  ├── Blog Post Template\n  └── Social Media Caption Generator\n\nCustomer Support:\n  ├── Response to Complaint\n  ├── FAQ Generator\n  └── Escalation Message"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Strategy 5: Role-Based Organization"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Organize prompts by function\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Role-based categories:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Productivity & Performance Management"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sales"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Marketing"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Engineering"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"HR"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Finance"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sales Role:\n  ├── Cold Email Template\n  ├── Follow-up Message\n  └── Negotiation Script\n\nMarketing Role:\n  ├── Campaign Planning\n  ├── Content Calendar\n  └── Press Release Draft"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tagging System"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-Dimensional Tags"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Use multiple tags for flexible filtering\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tag categories:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use case"},{"type":"text","text":" — Email, blog, code review, analysis\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tone"},{"type":"text","text":" — Formal, casual, technical, friendly\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Model"},{"type":"text","text":" — GPT-5, Claude, Llama, etc.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complexity"},{"type":"text","text":" — Simple, intermediate, advanced\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Length"},{"type":"text","text":" — Short, medium, long\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Industry"},{"type":"text","text":" — Healthcare, finance, tech, retail"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example prompt with tags:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt: Email Newsletter Generator\nTags:\n  - Use case: email, newsletter\n  - Tone: professional, engaging\n  - Model: Claude 3.5\n  - Complexity: intermediate\n  - Length: medium\n  - Industry: marketing"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Color-Coding for Quick Visual"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Tag or color code your prompts to quick access\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Color scheme:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"🟢 Green"},{"type":"text","text":" — High-performing, proven\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"🔵 Blue"},{"type":"text","text":" — For testing, experimental\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"🔴 Red"},{"type":"text","text":" — Deprecated, outdated\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"🟡 Yellow"},{"type":"text","text":" — Needs review, improving"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Template Structure"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Standard Entry Format"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Each entry should include:\""}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Component"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What to Include"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Purpose"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":